Good morning to all.<EOS> In the case of Atlantic Lottery Corporation, Inc. et al.
against Douglas Babstock et al., for the appellant, Atlantic Lottery
Corporation, Inc.: Julie Rosenthal, Mike Eizenga, Sarah Stoddar- Stoddart, I'm
